channel.title: Gate - dr. aquaman [trance]
channel.description:
[https://soundcloud.com/dr-aquaman/gate](https://soundcloud.com/dr-aquaman/gate)
![gate|500x500](upload://ftGHMXuJFqzkoKYzqhM3jB0kuTo.jpeg)
The musical direction of this instrumental track can not really be classified. I would say it's primarily trance with a few acid elements in the beginning but rather tracid but at 82 bpm. The track is very dark, sad and bassy. The melody is the most important thing like all my tracks. The origin is a piano piece. Check my tracklist for the original "other side". Enjoy listening...
